result.text:
“China’s Belt and Road Initiative, and China’s World Heritage”. Today’s recommendation comes to Xiamen’s Gulangyu Island.
Gulangyu Island is known as the “Museum of Architecture of All Nations”, with over 400 historical buildings open for public visit. It is Xiamen’s romantic commitment to bring the world cultural heritages to life and pass them on.
Nowadays, piano, music, fine arts and other cultural elements of #Gulangyu Island are becoming more prominent, and the century-old cultural accumulation is shining with new vitality.
#BeltRoad #WorldHeritage #Xiamen
